  "body": "For example, EIP-1 has `Motivation (*optional)` explicitly stated, but `Reference Implementation` doesn't have the `(*optional)` note.\r\n\r\nThe `Backwards Compatibility` section _seems_ optional (`All EIPs that [...] must`) but @lightclient usually marks it as required.\r\n\r\nWe should explicitly mark all optional sections with `(optional)`, and explain the requirements in the following text.",
